{"tid":1154844,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"飛機廣播傳來BTS防彈少年團歌曲...是機長放的！貼心暖舉原因曝光","createTime":"2019-05-14T14:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T09:40:46.000Z","uid":74065,"like":19,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c981a271d8cea5bbb9dbabd1062a3e7690433ff0","tid":1154844,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:16:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>南韓炙手可熱的偶像男團BTS防彈少年團，正在美國準備巡迴演唱會，日前有粉絲準備飛往芝加哥的演唱會現場，在機艙坐定就聽到廣播傳來熟悉的偶像主打歌曲，讓該名粉絲差點在飛機上跟著合唱，而接著機長的暖心提醒，更是讓全場爆笑出來。</strong></span>而機長此舉原因也接著曝光。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4094/d4094407.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4094%2Fd4094407.jpg&h=aa543104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團美國巡迴唱到芝加哥。（圖／翻攝自防彈少年團推特）<br />\n<br />\n推特帳號「taextrivia」分享她準備前往芝加哥觀看BTS演唱會，她寫下，「不誇張，整台飛機幾乎都是要去看演唱會的Army（BTS粉絲名稱）。」這時候飛機廣播傳來熟悉的旋律，一聽正是BTS經典夯曲《Fake Love》，讓粉絲又驚又喜！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/taextrivia/status/1127210596741668864?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1127210596741668864&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190514%2F1444546.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftaextrivia%2Fstatus%2F1127210596741668864%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1127210596741668864%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F20190514%252F1444546.htm&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=1df3e34a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftaextrivia%2Fstatus%2F1127210596741668864%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1127210596741668864%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F20190514%252F1444546.htm&h=ceaf68f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/taextrivia/status/1127210596741668864?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1127210596741668864&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190514%2F1444546.htm</a><br />\n該名粉絲隨著旋律差點大合唱時，音樂中斷、機長說話了，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「對那些不知道誰是BTS或是不在乎的人，抱歉！」向那些可能一頭霧水的乘客們特別致歉，幽默舉動讓粉絲笑出來。</strong></span>等到飛機降落後，同一首歌再度播放出來，這回機長貼心廣播，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「希望你們參加BTS的演唱會順利，歡迎來到芝加哥，祝玩得愉快！」讓不少在場粉絲都爆出歡呼聲。</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4094/d4094408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4094%2Fd4094408.jpg&h=737423a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團芝加哥演唱會吸引大批粉絲前往朝聖。（圖／翻攝自防彈少年團推特）<br />\n<br />\n粉絲也在推特分享，其實那班飛機的機長不但知道BTS是誰，原來他的女兒也要去這場BTS演唱會追星，等於是力挺女兒喜愛偶像。吸引其他粉絲留言，「為何我不是搭到這班飛機？」、「我也想要擁有這種爸爸」、「哪家航空我想要搭！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/taextrivia/status/1127248784797458438?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1127248784797458438&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190514%2F1444546.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftaextrivia%2Fstatus%2F1127248784797458438%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1127248784797458438%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F20190514%252F1444546.htm&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=9f236a95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftaextrivia%2Fstatus%2F1127248784797458438%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1127248784797458438%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F20190514%252F1444546.htm&h=7e027b7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/taextrivia/status/1127248784797458438?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1127248784797458438&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190514%2F1444546.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c68a44f432dd8c27522d3c2e85d7f5a742f6f765","tid":1154844,"uid":223790,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27